  "text": "We have looked for the relative abundance of each supposed thermal transition in the total calorimetric enthalpy (see Table 1 ) adapting the idea of Briere et al. [CITATION_1] . On the basis of these results, it can be seen quite well that the most affected muscle compounds are the myosin tail (T m2 ) and F-actin (T m3 and T m4 ).",
